title: Sprout Salad
description: For anyone wanting to work more sprouts into their meals, this is one of the best salads I've made in a long time. It includes mung bean sprouts, avocado, arugula, yogurt, and toasted almonds. So many good ingredients and incredibly tasty! Continue reading Sprout Salad on 101 Cookbooks
author: Heidi Swanson
